keyFacts: A meeting titled 'Epstein Pre-Meet' was scheduled for December 14, 2007, in Alex Acosta's office.
Alex Acosta, then U.S. Attorney for the Southern District of Florida (USAFLS), was the organizer of this personal-classified meeting.
The meeting involved another individual referenced only by a document identifier (EFTA00013475), whose identity is not disclosed in this entry.
